</span> 標題：拖網、圍網（dragnet, seine）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： חֵרֶם</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： cherem)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:5\">EZK 26:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:14\">EZK 26:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek32:3\">EZK 32:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek47:10\">EZK 47:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:15\">HAB 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:16\">HAB 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:17\">HAB 1:17</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： σαγήνη</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： sagēnē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:47\">MAT 13:47</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>拖網是垂直懸掛在水中的一張很長的網，上邊緣有浮子，下邊緣有重物。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>拖網由船上或岸邊的人拉拽收網。在拖網的兩端都被拉到船上或岸上之後，所圍區域裡面的魚就被困住。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在不要求區分各種漁網的語言中，可以使用表示「網」的統稱。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:47\">MAT 13:47</a> ，網的實際樣式並不是很重要。重要的是網非常大，能夠網住許多不同種類的魚。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:15\">HAB 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:16\">HAB 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:17\">HAB 1:17</a> ：參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.3.1.1 手拋網 (casting net)&lt;REALIA:1.3.1.1&gt;</a> 中的註解。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
